人架咩？ 個個掛住自己走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冷氣軍師，我知我廢，對唔住前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"歎冷氣仲好意思屌人無勇氣<br />\n你唔出嚟幫手就出少句聲當幫忙<br />\n前線已經好大壓力仲要俾你班撚樣指指點點"},{"pid":"5a46426a955ffdfa760bf88696241cc561f84188","tid":1525640,"uid":171234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:11:45.000Z","msg":"呢個世界果然文化多元，大家要好好向唔同文化學習，但同時抗拒劣質文化呀！"},{"pid":"bd8d819a9f447e3c9f0a1664dfd39d3daa24c9d9","tid":1525640,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2cc3fa5024327f053780ad8309d6cb0225749f48","tid":1525640,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc11a0741a4deb5d120f82c33f4c360d7d57565c","tid":1525640,"uid":53106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:12:43.000Z","msg":"經過8.31，真係要以武制暴，一個手足有事其他就一擁而上，救得一個得一個！夢中見！"},{"pid":"ef99080b2a786513b22e24460bf92c2dd8976364","tid":1525640,"uid":17866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d3973e68bbc0533711a6ffd6651455ac45575086","tid":1525640,"uid":259963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7b3c4d234c99e650c8afc544a234285f8e0c769","tid":1525640,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00eee819f659cff7d23fa379be063e3add0f2942","tid":1525640,"uid":259963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:41:37.000Z","msg":"果d係廢老無錯<br />\n但依到好多長輩睇<br />\n佢地會覺得連登仔話埋佢地架<br />\n<br />\n最好加多2個字<br />\n藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:53:37.000Z","msg":"人地出手打柒你都叫廢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班full gear出比撚到全滅人地都無事，我係咪真心左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:59:20.000Z","msg":"首先定義左乜野係廢<br />\n<br />\n班廢老大搖大擺恃住有黑警係背後唔會拉佢地而打人，依d叫狐假虎威<br />\n<br />\nFull gear義士明知會比人拉比人打都要企出黎。佢地尋晚未必做得好好，有改善空間。但<span style=\"color: red;\">絕不割𥱊！</span><br />\n<br />\n你認為邊樣係廢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"阿哥，唔好打咁多飛機啦....<br />\n你講個班廢老係6月前我都幾肯定有咩事就郁手，根本唔關有無狗撐腰事。人地慣左唔順你咪郁手，係你地呢班自稱和平既弱者先鐘會用口水核彈攻擊人<br />\n<br />\n尋晚個個Masked,full gear，已經係出開去，話狗都唔驚啦？咁人地有狗撐腰真係影響到你個下敢唔敢郁手咩？<br />\n根本就係廢，無撚用到連自己廢都唔敢認。<br />\n認廢有幾閒？唔認清自己廢，做得差點會去諗改善空間？ <br />\n<br />\n次次都比一百個理由自己雖敗猶榮，安慰唔係自己既錯，盡左力啦點點點，所以咪成世都咁廢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖敗猶榮係人地評論既，唔係你自己同自己講架"},{"pid":"c7c803dca72679f30e99fe36f86c726c64790e0c","tid":1525640,"uid":237295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:13:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾桶方案"},{"pid":"c03a9709f435f1730b3420d66079bf2c24311f2d","tid":1525640,"uid":236473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ef36a4099b816d31bb099d6e880761664f3a525f","tid":1525640,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6da85c03e19d89f20a7a4758cc69d078bb9c59","tid":1525640,"uid":42920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"去佢地過黎香港幫拖～～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca4012da9d677185862293f87ae71fb05db3ed5","tid":1525640,"uid":45471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:15:16.000Z","msg":"幾好呀，係香港亂掉垃圾係犯法<br />\n但垃圾桶方案只不過係將垃圾掉番入垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7a2f6901bc0144541fb742789e9648e30d5419","tid":1525640,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"點解烏克蘭咁窮但咁多靚女"},{"pid":"f2943068f65dddac392f89a9e65f83a4e4e4faeb","tid":1525640,"uid":174322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e91d38b9e65dc63adb7113ce366341c5fd16a6","tid":1525640,"uid":288714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ee7970a94ee07bee7ccb34d25df32ffcc50c90","tid":1525640,"uid":206923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"尋日香港既事，除左年輕既烏克蘭政治人員有留意，大部分知識分子都有留意，而尋晚終於吸引烏克蘭酒鬼們既目光。<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥民族酒友們，包括我條女，都係問我點解比人打唔還手？(我條女話如果佢係地鐵比人打，佢會抆刀，而且以後都會帶刀出入，聽完之後我諗會同佢鬧少d交)<br />\n<br />\n咁我就好努力解釋香港帶刀犯法，香港人好和平，香港人講道理，點知比佢地吊到飛天。(當然戰鬥民族個道理同我地個道理有出入。)<br />\n<br />\n然後佢地問香港人點解唔等機會翻枱還拖？<br />\n我除左答愛好和平之外都唔知點講。<br />\n<br />\n經過好幾rd 激辯劈酒之後，咁佢地推介扔xx入垃圾桶，影相影片日日扔。我聽完都係果句啦，大家文化背景唔同，烏克蘭做到，香港未必做得到，周9圍天眼，黑警又惡撚過日軍。但佢地話呢招又唔傷人又無殺人放火，我就解釋佢地知，亂掉垃圾係香港可能犯法啦。<br />\n咁當然又比佢地吊啦。<br />\n<br />\n然後都係飲酒9up，咁結論呢，就係烏克蘭酒友一致認同垃圾桶方案係最溫和但有效既方法。<br />\n<br />\n利申:我係和理非，我唔支持暴力，唔支持違法行為，但我支持5大訴求，支持香港人，我只係分享轉述烏克蘭酒友既說話同對香港現況既回應，並無煽動，鼓吹，誘惑任何人亂掉垃圾及任何違法行為。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2fDmh3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2fDmh3p.jpg&h=60e94ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比張女兵支持下大家(網友圖片)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"需引入戰鬥文族同革命民族入嚟抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0989d8a6caf4e4d7808157efa76eccbb8052ae7","tid":1525640,"uid":279145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cda3f2bc5ead5616522cd7ee4cf35048bf5dac","tid":1525640,"uid":85822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"重點：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比人打要還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n善用d酒飲唔哂就掉垃圾桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"154113c809233be60eb9a733e46ebe5b19ef2b4d","tid":1525640,"uid":245713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"係膽小，唔係和平"},{"pid":"2584a956a475eb8c848e419787b13c8d9a273052","tid":1525640,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"332d29a0edb5e94e8c5caf2ce541df2d32ebe230","tid":1525640,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"471896d42449683cb05f77d2dde172164c6c5d96","tid":1525640,"uid":73596,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"其實我都認同，點解俾人打唔還手，做咩俾黑警速龍追，個個都雞飛狗走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到有手足俾人㩒低唔上前幫拖，由得佢地俾人拉？<br />\n<br />\n說好既齊上齊落呢？ 我地唔係好多人架咩？ 個個掛住自己走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冷氣軍師，我知我廢，對唔住前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:27:58.000Z","msg":"你以為勇武嘅武力值都好高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f7d1d32785652afad1b49ad8e8249d16be21632","tid":1525640,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f480b78ce1005978e4f16b081e22e89ebe947b5d","tid":1525640,"uid":237295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41b436234ce515fa6b04b29a3e3c7f9c0fa0f959","tid":1525640,"uid":150021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1810d3deb70fa556cd422ae1beabbb8dc6d01c3c","tid":1525640,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"96ef57567806861f38456d60319f0969ddde2039","tid":1525640,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"點識ukraine女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1934a6b0cd1c24789d1eae30d91ea824ebf3cf0d","tid":1525640,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"31fec1d55b38b68d9556723858f9e7246c4be70c","tid":1525640,"uid":49853,"like":8,"disli