/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"popo<br />\n麻包袋完掉落垃圾桶"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"咁撚花功夫，一刀桶落去/燒9死佢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:47:18.000Z","msg":"講就易, 邊個敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfc62f9c15827939f802f93a06ad6b14f6fa4f1","tid":1525640,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ded6c9aa6028ea6acbaf4fed595bcb7e78a808a6","tid":1525640,"uid":99172,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4c4f0855ecd764d0f4764be40475f1df82350775","tid":1525640,"uid":62811,"like":206,"dislike":3,"score":203,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"比啲時間啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日見到火光熊熊已經好振奮人心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:50:26.000Z","msg":"真心覺得火魔法師大部分都係popo <br />\n得佢地先夠膽袋住咁多酒周街走<br />\n而且啲火扔極都唔中黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"同埋昨日啲火勁好多"},{"pid":"2b1f4e32229c8483f2103f4c076aa49c27b244ec","tid":1525640,"uid":26619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a330bb5241819ecfc41c4602c9aa1586ced82264","tid":1525640,"uid":120084,"like":82,"dislike":10,"score":72,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭d女女仲會唔會考慮嫁黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:08:09.000Z","msg":"我日本老婆話，如果我係香港俾警察整死左，會帶炸雞入警處同死黑警一鑊熟。聽到我真係喊出來，有人肯為我死。所以我覺得香港人太醒目，太懂計代價，咩都怕。人生都就完，先發現最後咩都無做。end game啦，重就著就著。"},{"pid":"e303534d90453055de43a77e264a7c40e3aee30b","tid":1525640,"uid":52100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"香港民族性好難搞 道德撚 怕事撚會鬧左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要盡快令